{"tid":2194474,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大摩指Tesla股價最壞情況或只值10美元　傳蘋果曾出價至240美元","createTime":"2020-09-08T13:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T22:05:32.000Z","uid":21872,"like":10,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e361e648a0d39cf7fa8cd217e42f6de97cb818","tid":2194474,"uid":21872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:49:25.000Z","msg":"美國電動車生產商特斯拉（Tesla）股價跌跌不休，股價今年累挫約39%，投行摩根士丹利近日再發表報告，睇淡Tesla股價，指最壞情況Tesla股價要跌95%。<br />\n<br />\n報告指，Tesla正日益依賴中國市場，但受中美貿易摩擦升溫影響，料Tesla於中國市場的銷量無法達標，更有可能只有原先估計的一半。大摩分析員Adam Jonas表示，中國市場銷量的減少，加上負債增加，和高層離任、電動車減價等潛在負面因素，認為Tesla在最壞情況下，股價將大幅下挫，股價或只值10美元。"},{"pid":"63612dd90eb9cb2d9fd3311038bff6c7bd7a1e0c","tid":2194474,"uid":175540,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"大摩想入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2964e60ac14ba794df0c4d8d248ba5f0cbf63cd3","tid":2194474,"uid":21872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63612dd90eb9cb2d9fd3311038bff6c7bd7a1e0c","tid":2194474,"uid":175540,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"大摩想入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:53:47.000Z","msg":"酒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f1060d600b058188b8fbfb51a15482021e7f16","tid":2194474,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63612dd90eb9cb2d9fd3311038bff6c7bd7a1e0c","tid":2194474,"uid":175540,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"大摩想入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:54:03.000Z","msg":"佢要做低個價先入"},{"pid":"0522dbbc3f489ce1d4730e7a2d6c9e1b7e9e06a9","tid":2194474,"uid":957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"又回帶"},{"pid":"5fa4262c94a04ed8b401be503a76af5809b2e1a5","tid":2